      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified material test reports for production Ti-6Al-4V bar stock. Geometric inputs from calibrated CMM measurements of production implants. Uncertainty in inputs propagated to QoI uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield stress derived from certified test reports (mean ± 1σ across five material lots). Screw geometry from CMM measurements (±0.005 mm). UVAL computed from combined input uncertainty using Monte Carlo sampling (N=1000 runs). Input uncertainty contribution to total uval: 3.1% for stiffness QoI. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
