      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions and loading replicate experimental fixture geometry and loading protocol. Fixture compliance characterized and incorporated into model.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 fixture geometry modeled explicitly including UHMWPE blocks and loading fixtures. Fixture compliance measured experimentally (compliance = 0.0023 mm/N) and incorporated as boundary condition correction. Screw seating depth matched to experimental measurements ±0.1 mm. Equivalency of input parameters confirmed at gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
