      "rationale": "Three QoIs selected directly map to FDA guidance for pedicle screw 510(k) submissions: construct stiffness characterizes elastic behavior, yield force identifies onset of plastic deformation, and force at 40 mm displacement represents post-yield structural integrity. All QoIs are clinically and regulatorily relevant. Gradation 3 achieved."
