    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved gradation 2 vs. required gradation 3) is acknowledged and documented. Given that all three primary QoIs pass the E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion across N=11 specimens from two independent laboratories, the assessment team judges the overall body of evidence sufficient to support regulatory use of the FEA model for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw compression-bending COU at Medium assurance level.",
